Description: Fast, Pythonic way to build MCP servers and clients
 The Model Context Protocol (MCP) provides a standardized way to
 connect AI agents to tools and data. FastMCP makes it easy to build
 MCP applications with clean, Pythonic code.
 .
 FastMCP provides:
  * Clean decorator-based API for defining tools, resources and prompts
  * Automatic schema generation and validation
  * Built-in support for various transport protocols
  * Middleware for error handling, logging, and rate limiting
  * OAuth and authentication support
  * OpenAPI integration
 .
 This package provides the Python 3 library.
